[normal]phs
[normal] 5, 20, 25, 26 and 27. This therefore excludes 
[normal]paragraphs 6 (community care), 21 (abuse of position or powers by a public authority), 22 (breach of Convention r
[normal]ights by a public authority) 
[normal]and 43 (claims
[normal] under the Equality Act 2010
[normal]). 
